{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "16.1",
      "line_index": 16,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "18ba35c2",
      "speaker": "モエ",
      "ja": "お・じ・さ～ん♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "18.0",
      "line_index": 18,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "adff3dd1",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "うっ……モ、モエ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "20.1",
      "line_index": 20,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "3bdd169",
      "speaker": "モエ",
      "ja": "ひど～い、こんなかわいい女の子が話しかけてあげたのに、そこまで警戒する～？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "22.0",
      "line_index": 22,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "89a7d5a4",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（まったく……心にもないことを言って……何を考えているかわからないからモエは苦手だ……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "24.0",
      "line_index": 24,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e02b73b",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（でも、もしかしたら偏見かもしれないし……。）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "26.1",
      "line_index": 26,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "5f28809e",
      "speaker": "モエ",
      "ja": "ねえ、ところでデートしない？♥　あんた達が助けた星を見に行こうよ♪",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "28.0",
      "line_index": 28,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e6ab5239",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "デートだと……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "30.0",
      "line_index": 30,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cde1b301",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（モエは混乱やトラブルを好み平和を嫌悪する性格だからな……普通にデートのお誘いなどしてくる筈がない……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "32.0",
      "line_index": 32,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "24e03af8",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（やはり偏見だとしても警戒するにこしたことはない。）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "36.1",
      "line_index": 36,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "19fdf5c5",
      "speaker": "モエ",
      "ja": "なにここ♪　人が多いしヘンな店ちょ～並んでるんですけど～♪",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "38.0",
      "line_index": 38,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "76f9f553",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "40.1",
      "line_index": 40,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "c931825f",
      "speaker": "モエ",
      "ja": "それにしても、あんなに警戒しておいて結局ついてくるなんて、だっさ～♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "42.0",
      "line_index": 42,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7a5d4cac",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "じゃあそもそもなんで誘ったんだよ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "44.1",
      "line_index": 44,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "ddd959f",
      "speaker": "モエ",
      "ja": "あっ！　ねえ、あそこのアイスクリーム買ってぇ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "46.0",
      "line_index": 46,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8c5964d6",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "無視の上にお強請りかよ……まったく……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "48.0",
      "line_index": 48,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6efbd759",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（でも断ったら何言われるかわからないし……仕方ないから、買ってやるか。）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "50.1",
      "line_index": 50,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "9dbdf059",
      "speaker": "モエ",
      "ja": "わ～い♥　おじさんやさし～♥　それじゃあいただきま～す♥　はむっ♥　ん～～～♥　おいし～♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "52.0",
      "line_index": 52,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "506d5c5e",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "危ない！　おい気をつけろよ、人並みに押しつぶされるところだったじゃないか",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "54.1",
      "line_index": 54,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "43dc96df",
      "speaker": "モエ",
      "ja": "ふーん？　下僕おじさんにしては気が利くじゃん",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "56.0",
      "line_index": 56,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "59a27a66",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "えっ……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "58.0",
      "line_index": 58,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5291e0c4",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（いきなり手を繋いできたりして……なんだか変な気持ちになってしまうじゃないか……。）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "60.1",
      "line_index": 60,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "b34275a6",
      "speaker": "モエ",
      "ja": "ほら♥　行くわよ下僕おじさん♥　今度はクレープ買ってぇ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "62.0",
      "line_index": 62,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3ced89c8",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "おい！　そんなに手を引っ張るなって！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "64.1",
      "line_index": 64,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "7c82e56c",
      "speaker": "モエ",
      "ja": "もっと色々なところを見て回るんだからグズグズしないのっ♥　こっちこっち♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "77.0",
      "line_index": 77,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "46e1699f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "何だかんだで祭りを楽しんじゃって……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "79.0",
      "line_index": 79,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "dd885085",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（モエもこうしていればただの女の子なんだが……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "81.1",
      "line_index": 81,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "39859b",
      "speaker": "モエ",
      "ja": "……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "83.0",
      "line_index": 83,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "c80ce4c8",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "……んっ？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "85.1",
      "line_index": 85,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "9100eef4",
      "speaker": "モエ",
      "ja": "……つまんないね、モア",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "87.0",
      "line_index": 87,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f39d545",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（うっ……さっきまではしゃいでいたのが嘘のように、冷めた目で当たりを見て……。）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "89.0",
      "line_index": 89,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3696736a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（モエの本当の気持ちって……どこにあるんだ？）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "91.1",
      "line_index": 91,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "ddbc9928",
      "speaker": "モエ",
      "ja": "はぁぁ……つまんないつまんない……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "93.0",
      "line_index": 93,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "99373e81",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（でも……危険すぎるリリアンのモエ……そのどこか暗い感じが逆に魅力的というか……。）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "95.0",
      "line_index": 95,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5507e92a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（いつかモエの本当の気持ちを知りたいな……。）",
      "zh": ""
    }
  ]
}
